summary: IDK WHY OR HOW but little kids just seem to flock to me at taylor concerts?? at 1989 we had these two angels next to us and they...
body:
IDK WHY OR HOW but little kids just seem to flock to me at taylor concerts?? at 1989 we had these two angels next to us and they got up and danced with us even tho their mum kept saying “sit down we’re not here to dance” BUT TEHY DID IT ANYWAY SUCK THAT MUM

and then at rep melbourne these other two girls asked about our costumes and where we were going and then on the train they got surprised with tickets and ran over to us screaming “WE’RE GOING TO TAYLOR SWIFT WITH YOU!!”

and finally at rep brisbane i had another little girl sitting with her mum in my row and when i got up to dance in the aisle to shake it off she came with me and we just danced together and had such a good time and just omg im so glad i get to share these little moments with kids who are the age i was when i first discovered taylor it’s just… magical
